.<br />\n<br />\n我聽到好多同事616都有出嚟，雖然唔敢大事張揚...我自己都行咗6個鐘，依少少不便其實唔算咩！我都都想發表「我地作為市民」嘅聲音，但只係因為我地都要為我地嘅職責負責任，維持社會運作唔可以隨便罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前係我地私底下嘅Whatsapp group直頭有人問會唔會去野餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />某程度上我地接受不便，等於間接支持其他市民代替我地發聲，我地就只可以離開我地岡位後變返「市民」再發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d987252aa48985e773ff1bec53b1b2082d158d11","tid":1247543,"uid":25811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:09:03.000Z","msg":"以後9點後先佔，咁就冇人話你阻佢返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad61727d382af99e4b8ea0b16ee0a9d45f30d3f6","tid":1247543,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:10:44.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n真係有用 做唔到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d380147f313068e8f78246802afe58d2daa671","tid":1247543,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6528302d2a515a163482c24a6c11028128515281","tid":1247543,"uid":265066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2f3af8cb678339f9fff9746ad53b5d41d929b9","tid":1247543,"uid":164372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b05a5f40aadac26aebc45ffe365236888d085e6","tid":1247543,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eab78bbab065bfaa11e3e764a57097e914a8f662","tid":1247543,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:41:09.000Z","msg":"成功解放公務員勞動監獄, 公務員為表謝意支持打倒邪惡勢力"},"citedBy":